{"tid":2176454,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【陳彥霖死因研訊】同學稱彥霖活潑開朗 失蹤前稱：一齊做想做嘅嘢 拍片錄歌開channel","createTime":"2020-08-27T05:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T16:29:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e676513daa92690fc837dc02c8b423e644c2d346","tid":2176454,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:55:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/NHAGBRP7UNF7REODGAOQOW364M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FNHAGBRP7UNF7REODGAOQOW364M%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97ZvpkwzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=d1d18ff5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FNHAGBRP7UNF7REODGAOQOW364M%2F&h=123bf042\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/NHAGBRP7UNF7REODGAOQOW364M/</a><br />\n<br />\n曾參與反送中集會的15歲職訓局青年書院女生陳彥霖，去年9月底離奇赤裸浮屍海面，警方及後指死因無可疑。死因庭今繼續研訊，彥霖的知專同學供稱，彥霖於去年9月16日開始上學，起初數天與同學相處得非常開心。她印象中，彥霖非常活潑開朗，而且話很多，非常願意分享生活，「乜都講，同邊個都講」，不似有隱瞞不開心的心事，反而非常期待上學。彥霖曾透露跟家人關係不算好、男友在獄中服刑，又自言有參與社會運動。"},{"pid":"28e011e7b29677976a3734e8a06ba75c700463de","tid":2176454,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:55:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74517c682367193ca9509807eecdf754f73523e","tid":2176454,"uid":198714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:55:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c46713af7a2d6916027a0dc84c57fa8ed1eec19a","tid":2176454,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T05:55:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=